      • withAnchor

        public ReportExecutionOptions.Builder withAnchor(@Nullable
                                                 java.lang.String anchor)
        Allows to start export execution starting from specified anchor. Anchor name. Has lower priority, than pages parameter. If pages parameter is specified, then anchor is ignored. If pages parameter isn't specified, then export will generate a page, where is an anchor with corresponding name.
        Parameters:
        anchor - the entry point of exact page
        Returns:
        builder for convenient configuration
